article_title: UN official does not expect aid to flow more easily into north Gaza.
sentence: Georgios  Petropoulos  says  he  doesn't  expect  humanitarian  aid  to  enter  northern  Gaza  more  easily  now  that  Yahya  Sinwar  is  dead.

sentence: He  paints  a  bleak  picture  of  the  situation,  describing  having  seen  "children  dying  on  the  floors  of  hospital"  because  medicines  can't  reach  them.
